sub_title: Communication Science Student at the University of Amsterdam
summary:
What about me?

I am a 24 years old student at the University of Amsterdam. 
An outgoing person, passionate about psychology, politics, history and in love with photography/videography and music.
Living in Amsterdam and learning Dutch for the past 3 years.

I am an enthusiastic person with experience in hospitality, office administrative, broadcasting productions, commercial productions.
I am always willing to take on a new challenge with excitement. 
I enjoy working in a group with more people and am always glad to help others. 
My professional qualities involve creativity, organizational skills, improvisation and independent problem solving.
